title: 55: The Summer Food Finds Chew & Tell Episode
itunes:title: The Summer Food Finds Chew & Tell Episode
description: It’s heating up out there, and we have just what you need to cool yourself right back down! In this episode, Lisa and the gang are taste testing healthy summer food finds so you don’t have to! Everything from salad kits and ice cream, to fruit bars and SO MUCH MORE! Plus the bite-sized treat that will have you running to the freezer aisle! So what are you waiting for? Push play now!!! www.hungry-girl.com/foodcast
